Quote:  ... they packed up and started for Oakden - ... found Mr. O. just preparing to ... take them some provisions it now began to rain and the party were not at all sorry to find themselves comfortably housed in Mr. O's snug little crib where after spending a very pleasant evening ... they turned in and slept soundly ...
